05:32.960 --> 05:34.600
Dasar cerpelai bodoh.

05:59.200 --> 06:01.760
Bulan Baru, dengarkan perintah.

06:05.960 --> 06:06.880
Pergilah.

06:08.000 --> 06:09.760
Aktifkan formasi sihir Nvwa

06:10.760 --> 06:13.120
dan biarkan empat pilar penyangga bumi

06:13.960 --> 06:15.160
menampakkan wujudnya.

06:15.760 --> 06:16.680
- Baik.
- Baik.

06:38.680 --> 06:39.520
Apakah kau melihat You Chi?

06:48.320 --> 06:49.800
- Wangyan.
- Can Yue.

06:52.000 --> 06:53.000
Canyue.

06:54.000 --> 06:54.840
Canyue.

06:56.960 --> 06:58.040
Hentikan dia.

07:00.040 --> 07:01.000
Canyue.

07:16.400 --> 07:17.280
Wangyan.

07:18.960 --> 07:20.480
