32:15.400 --> 32:16.440
Bintang Biduk Alkaid.

32:16.520 --> 32:17.400
Bentuk formasi.

34:39.520 --> 34:40.360
Guru.

35:05.320 --> 35:06.240
You Chi.

35:06.920 --> 35:07.880
Kakak Wu.

